    "causal_summary": "A user at spec-kit `v3.3.0.0` (or any version older than `v3.4.1.0`) has 6+ databases that drift out of alignment with their codebase: `context-index.sqlite` (memory FTS+vector, 134M+362M), `code-graph.sqlite` (51M structural index), `skill-graph.sqlite` (148K), `deep-loop-graph.sqlite` (84K coverage graphs), `speckit-eval.db` (16M ablation results), and `causaledges` table (in context-index, lazy-init)",
